### ============================================
### USERS (VTL + DynamoDB / in-memory fallback)
### ============================================

### Create User
POST http://localhost:4000/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "mutation { createUser(input: { name: \"Alice Smith\", email: \"alice@example.com\" }) { id name email createdAt } }"
}

###

### List Users
POST http://localhost:4000/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "{ listUsers { id name email createdAt } }"
}

###

### Get User
POST http://localhost:4000/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "query GetUser($id: ID!) { getUser(id: $id) { id name email createdAt } }",
  "variables": { "id": "REPLACE_WITH_USER_ID" }
}

###

### Update User (NONE datasource)
POST http://localhost:4000/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "mutation { updateUser(id: \"user-1\", input: { name: \"Alice Updated\", email: \"alice.new@example.com\" }) { id name email updatedAt } }"
}

###

### Delete User
POST http://localhost:4000/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "mutation { deleteUser(id: \"REPLACE_WITH_USER_ID\") }"
}

