### ============================================
### INTROSPECTION
### ============================================

### Full Schema Introspection
POST http://localhost:4000/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "{ __schema { queryType { name fields { name } } mutationType { name fields { name } } } }"
}

###

### ============================================
### INVENTORY (Java Lambda)
### ============================================

### Check Stock
POST http://localhost:4000/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "{ checkStock(productId: \"prod-001\") { productId productName totalStock reserved available inStock } }"
}

###

### Reserve Stock
POST http://localhost:4000/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "mutation { reserveStock(input: { productId: \"prod-001\", orderId: \"order-99\", quantity: 5 }) { reservationId productId orderId quantity status createdAt } }"
}

###

### Release Stock (use reservationId from above)
POST http://localhost:4000/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "mutation ReleaseStock($id: ID!) { releaseStock(reservationId: $id) { reservationId status releasedAt } }",
  "variables": { "id": "REPLACE_WITH_RESERVATION_ID" }
}

###

### Adjust Stock (+10)
POST http://localhost:4000/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "mutation { adjustStock(input: { productId: \"prod-003\", adjustment: 10, reason: \"Restock delivery\" }) { productId previousStock adjustment currentStock reason adjustedAt } }"
}

###

### Adjust Stock (-5)
POST http://localhost:4000/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "mutation { adjustStock(input: { productId: \"prod-002\", adjustment: -5, reason: \"Damaged items\" }) { productId previousStock adjustment currentStock reason adjustedAt } }"
}

###
